425
00:30:24,050 --> 00:30:25,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau butuh koneksi?</font>

426
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:27,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau ingin mendapatkan jabatan pemerintah di sana?</font>

427
00:30:29,790 --> 00:30:30,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu benar?</font>

428
00:30:30,830 --> 00:30:31,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya</font>

429
00:30:32,130 --> 00:30:34,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah sebabnya kami bertengkar. Kami punya alasan.</font>

430
